    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/6a08049ee07df4e321f350c85a0cb2e6.webp?t=1732730132\" width=198 height=16 /></span><br>The placing, stacking and attacking board game, where your goal is to capture every one of your opponent's pieces.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/945739689242d397ffb5cd6e8c18ba94.poster.avif?t=1732730132\" width=508 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/945739689242d397ffb5cd6e8c18ba94.webm?t=1732730132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/945739689242d397ffb5cd6e8c18ba94.mp4?t=1732730132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game starts with a placement phase where players take turns placing roughly half of their pieces on the board.<br><br>From there, the main phase of the game begins, where both players try to capture eachothers pieces. During this main phase, players can place new pieces anywhere on their side of the board. Players can also stack pieces on top of eachother to grant their pieces additional range.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/5f88bb92cd9f2ee0393ed33096d18195.webp?t=1732730132\" width=399 height=18 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/d1dd6a5fa125f620fbd80363bc0da568.poster.avif?t=1732730132\" width=500 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/d1dd6a5fa125f620fbd80363bc0da568.webm?t=1732730132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/d1dd6a5fa125f620fbd80363bc0da568.mp4?t=1732730132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Once you have gotten the hang of it, try your skill on the competitive ranked ladder that features a one of a kind percentile based Elo system to see where you stack up against the rest of the community. Compete for glory and the chance to uncover the hidden super ranks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/dd1f899fb78a437b5193c75a106291f2.webp?t=1732730132\" width=279 height=15 /></span><br>Vantageous contains an in-game lobby system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/693f2664b59380b9f3e1f6088fda1e64.webp?t=1732730132\" width=195 height=15 /></span><br>Try out our quick-match queue where you can play casually against players of similar skill to you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/2465a35b97b2d30ea40d3b34072d5c5b.webp?t=1732730132\" width=349 height=15 /></span><br>Test your skills against the different CPU's.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714210/extras/08d81b014955c03ca0f7d98dae80732a.webp?t=1732730132\" width=432 height=15 /></span><br>Try out our in depth tutorial to make sure you understand the basics.",
